AVMedia AIO Softwares [deepstatus]




Audio Converter v7.2.6

AV Audio Converter is a media file conversion tool which is well
documented and suitable for absolute beginners and advanced users
alike. The program will be your best assistant to help you not only
convert between audio files like MP3, WMA, WAV, AAC, MP2, AC3,
and more, but also extract soundtracks from all popular movies or
music videos, such as MP4, 3GP, FLV, AVI, etc. with perfect sound
quality. You can convert multiple files in a single batch, regardless
of their source and target formats. In addition, the formats conversion
is performed without any temporary files, allowing lightning speed.


Audio Editor v7.5.1

AV Audio Editor is full-featured digital audio editing software that
offers a variety of audio recording, mixing, editing, analyzing and
effects processing possibilities. It provides an intuitive, easy-to-use
interface and is designed for the everyday user. It has dozens of
amazing audio effects and tools for converting audio files into
different formats, including MP3, WMA, WAV, Ogg Vorbis and many others.
If you're using audio for anything - websites, PowerPoint presentations,
Flash animations, AV Audio Editor will take your creations to the next
level.


Audio Merger v6.5.6

AV Audio Merger is an easy and fast audio tool which allows you to merge
multiple audio files of different formats into a single one with high
quality. A wide range of audio formats can be input and converted to the
most popular audio formats like MP3, WMA, WAV and OGG. The merger can
also be used as an audio converter to help you convert almost all
formats to the one of your choice. The operation of the tool is simple
and straightforward. Just click "Merge" or "Convert", the software will
do the rest job for you!


Audio Recorder v6.5.6

AV Audio Recorder is a compact audio recorder utility that allows
recording audio data from various inputs like microphone, vinyl records,
audio CDs, your favorite video game, Internet broadcasts, programs like
Real Player and other input lines on a sound card. Friendly wizard-styled
interface makes recording easy and convenient for every user.


Burning Prov6 v5.6

AV Burning Pro is a powerful disc suite for burning CD/DVD/Blu-Ray/HD-DVD
media, copy audio CD & create ISO images. AV Burning Studio supports all
types of optical storage media (including CD-R/RW, DVD-R/RW, DVD+R/RW,
BD-R/RE, HD-DVD-R/RW and DVD-RAM) as well as a wide variety of burning
hardware. AV Burning Pro has a Quick Start Wizard for novice users to
simplify frequently used operations to save much time spending on
finding a function.


Video Converter v6.5.6

Incredibly easy to use for both novices and pros, AV Video Converter
brings you all the capabilities to make polished video: convert video
of all popular formats like AVI, MPEG, WMV, DivX, MP4, H.264/AVC,
AVCHD, MKV, RM, MOV, XviD, 3GP, etc. and transform between MP3, WMA,
WAV, RA, M4A, AAC, AC3, OGG and more audios. Luxurious optimized
profiles are provided to make your movies and music played easily
on PSP, PS3, iPod, iPhone, Apple TV, Xbox and other digital devices.

In addition, AV Video Converter is also a handy YouTube downloader and
converter which means you can save whatever YouTube videos you like
- music videos, sports videos, new film trailers and funny videos to
your computer and convert them to the format for your portable devices
so that you can watch your videos whenever you want, even offline.
